snippet.title: Spacewing War 2 - Reveal + Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Play now!
https://gamespneuma.itch.io/spacewing-war-2-demo-1

Rise and Shine, it's 𝗦𝗽𝗮𝗰𝗲𝘄𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗪𝗮𝗿 𝟮!

In this demo, play as the charismatic Spacewing, a strange spaceship with eyes and limbs, and shoot your enemies up as you make your way through a galaxy of wonders!

Website: https://spacewingwar.com/
Twitter: https://x.com/AgusBarrero_
